WEBVTT

00:00:29.594 --> 00:00:33.515
all the way back to the year 300 BC,

00:00:33.539 --> 00:00:36.658
when a 13-year-old became the king

00:00:36.682 --> 00:00:41.125
of a remote, very poor
and very small Asian country.

00:00:41.475 --> 00:00:44.960
He dreamt of acquiring land,
riches and power

00:00:44.984 --> 00:00:46.651
through military conquest.

00:00:46.675 --> 00:00:48.058
And his design skills --

00:00:48.082 --> 00:00:49.905
improbable though it sounds --

00:00:49.929 --> 00:00:52.974
would be essential
in enabling him to do so.

00:00:53.605 --> 00:00:54.755
At the time,

00:00:54.779 --> 00:00:58.189
all weapons were made by hand
to different specifications.

